of crystal-waving nonsense.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1238878' id='t-1238878'>This is a pragmatic response
to good health.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1241522' id='t-1241522'>If you have good sleep,
it increases your concentration,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1244363' id='t-1244363'>attention, decision-making,
creativity, social skills, health.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1248372' id='t-1248372'>If you get sleep, it reduces
your mood changes, your stress,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1252721' id='t-1252721'>your levels of anger, your impulsivity,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1254878' id='t-1254878'>and your tendency to drink and take drugs.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1257495' id='t-1257495'>And we finished by saying</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1260354' id='t-1260354'>that an understanding
of the neuroscience of sleep</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1263504' id='t-1263504'>is really informing the way we think</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1266332' id='t-1266332'>about some of the causes
of mental illness,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1268866' id='t-1268866'>and indeed is providing us new ways</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1270946' id='t-1270946'>to treat these incredibly
debilitating conditions.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
