</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1275666' id='t-1275666'>Jim Butcher, the fantasy writer, said,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1279500' id='t-1279500'>&quot;Sleep is God. Go worship.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1281545' id='t-1281545'>And I can only recommend
